name: Eva's gaze
description:
from the collection "inside: darks"

I look at the sky
I extend my hands
Up and up
I close my eyes and open them
I have an apple in my hands
I bite it
I am condemned for this
I blink again
The clouds are in my hands
I bite the clouds
Then the sun
And the moon
And every one of stars
I have shed a little bit of everything in myself
I'm going to hell
And I will come out of heaven
I have even bitten God
And each of angels
I have bitten the devil
I blink
I stare at the sky
These are all there in me
  And yet I'm empty...
